name: [Private Servers] Sunshadow Falls II
description:
A remastered version of Alpha Authority old Sunshadow Falls fort, developed in the 3rd year of Alpha Authority's existent. Dedicated to being a more secure facility for our trainers.

[RULES]: Follow trainer instructions, try to participate in any votes that happen in-game, and feel free to try any glitches. Have fun!

[COMMANDS - MAIN ADMIN]: :cmds

[COMMANDS - PENDING HUB]:
!accept all/username (Accepts access into Reserved Server)
!decline all/username (Declines access into Reserved Server)
!add username (Adds Pending Hub Cohost Admin perms)
!remove username (Removes Pending Hub Cohost Admin perms)
!addgroup groupid (Whitelists a Group)
!removegroup groupid (Blacklists a Group)
!setgroups groupid groupid .. (Whitelists multiple groups)

[COMMANDS - HOLO (DEMO)]:
!cc - Commands
!hosts - Hosts
!cohost [Name] - Cohost players that are in-game.
!uncohost [Name] - Uncohost players that are in or out of game.
!weapons - Weapons
!weapon [Name] - Load weapon.

name: [Private Servers] BTC III
description:
Private server version of Bamboo Training Core III. This game allows private server owners to host events with the holo's admin. Every private server owner has the ability to set admins for their private server, which has no crossover with other private servers.

!start - Start round.
!end - End round.
!cc - Commands
!hosts - Hosts
!cohost [Name] - Cohost players that are in-game.
!uncohost [Name] - Uncohost players that are in or out of game.
!maps - Maps
!map [Name] - Load map.
!weapons - Weapons
!weapon [Name] - Load weapon.
!os [Number] - Set outscore.
